
flowchart LR
    A[New Problem] --> B[Analogy]

    B --> C[Surface Similarity]
    B --> D[Structural Similarity]

    C --> C1[Fast Mapping]
    C1 --> C2[Low Risk]
    C2 --> C3[Incremental Change]

    D --> D1[Deep Mapping]
    D1 --> D2[Higher Cognitive Cost]
    D2 --> D3[Potential Breakthrough]

    style C fill:#e6f2ff,stroke:#0033b2
    style D fill:#fff0e6,stroke:#b24700